\n就話你五毛 分化"},{"pid":"5ffacdf476fb0ee81eef93a2ee892f1dece21a79","tid":1777960,"uid":135274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T15:31:15.000Z","msg":"我甚至覺得蔡英文呢件事做政治炒作，然後唔理班義士都冇問題<br />\n<br />\n政治現實就係咁，真係唔幫你係道理黎<br />\n<br />\n你可以話呢樣野好唔道德，所以你普通人咁講一啲問題都冇，我甚至會舉腳支持<br />\n<br />\n但公眾人物，玩得政治就預咗要跟好污糟既rules，佢地係衰on9"},{"pid":"b77a3565f3c7e581e620197e54bdd2f1418ad79e","tid":1777960,"uid":263349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17569ad72d73df42daec533e472d32518ab20f8e","tid":1777960,"uid":338743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:57:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T15:39:43.000Z","msg":"雨傘之後 香港人拎住牌 去跪 台灣人 唔好信一國兩制<br />\n<br />\n我已經覺得 香港人係咪咁無尊嚴 點解要做到咁嘅地步<br />\n<br />\n人地日日係ptt 侮辱你 你真係覺得果d全部係網軍？<br />\n<br />\n但香港人依然 幫佢地到處簽外國聯署 <br />\n<br />\n想盡一切方法喚醒佢地  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f40eae5764a01fb070e0f48afe9f66a4b53243d","tid":1777960,"uid":61615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T15:42:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HYuyYam.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHYuyYam.jpg&h=d530771b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc717b2919364f5351a11605dc27c38aa7e75ec7","tid":1777960,"uid":35857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"254f9219b302056e12a38b0b9388e2cac4c8a1da","tid":1777960,"uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:46:03.000Z","msg":"fight for 支援<br />\nstand with 之鋒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T15:44:37.000Z","msg":"我agree樓主<br />\n小小要求唔係好過份啫<br />\n根本兩地就應該要互相幫助"},{"pid":"25bd97e32f57edcffa77623eb536a8644cafd727","tid":1777960,"uid":263349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea03a7166bfd972d9cf7234ca2f50fd23f5245ee","tid":1777960,"uid":343059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c85da1a271c03d8960b54260117f52bc4ef48f0","tid":1777960,"uid":157483,"like":2,"dislik